					"type": 23,
					"value": "The InParty for Shadowheart while in END_Main.\r\nMorphic Pool (Arrival)\r\nAstral Plane (Just after Netherbrain Confrontation)\r\nTadpole Choice (with Emperor in Astral Plane while making the choice to transform into a mind flayer)\r\nHigh Hall Interior (after Astral Plane, views of Nautiloids, Dragons, and a city in ruin)"
